                     <interp inst="t18440819-2013-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp> for stealing 1 pewter pot, value 1<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18440819-name-626" type="victimName">
